the handgun issue. As the Violence Policy Center
report states, the pro-gun lobby brushes the sub-

, ject away by saying that -victims would find a’

way to kill themselves “no matter what.” And,
since only 10 percent of suicide by firearms are
committed with weapons specifically purchased
